{"tid":1623650,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"緊急及蒙面法根本百利而無一害","createTime":"2019-10-05T00:43:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T06:49:22.000Z","uid":83732,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3469a9a75fb0f7d24e6f9e8455b5fb214a789e73","tid":1623650,"uid":83732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:43:57.000Z","msg":"中共根本蠢撚過豬，林鄭一返完大陸就立法，以為冇人上街等於解決左件事，而家終於十八區遍地開花裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一，提升大家<span style=\"color: red;\">危機意識</span><br />\n立左法之後大家好清楚你一蒙面黑警會即刻拉你<br />\n反而令大家行動小心<br />\n唔直接同黑警對峙<br />\n從而減低無謂送頭機會<br />\n包圍狗屋情況會大幅減少<br />\n<br />\n第二，讓大家重新<span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權</span><br />\n抗議對象一定係支持極權嘅每一個保皇狗<br />\n加埋一班老不死如梁愛滋譚餵豬班撚樣<br />\n見到最低限度要言語盡情侮辱<br />\n其餘方法前線手足決定<br />\n<br />\n第三，<span style=\"color: red;\">經濟懲罰</span>所有親中公司<br />\n大家見到登報支持政府嘅全部係大陸國企及一<br />\n眾奶共企業<br />\n佢地政商界擁有極大影響力<br />\n會左右政府嘅政策<br />\n該類深藍公司內部會逼迫甚至解僱立場不同員工<br />\n而你唔幫襯根本對佢地嘅短時間內嘅影響唔明顯<br />\n亦都冇可能動員咁多人每日搞佢哋<br />\n故呢排終於有朋友令佢地的起心肝重新裝修<br />\n一裝修座底要一兩個月<br />\n經濟損失嚴重<br />\n亦等裝修界朋友有工開<br />\n<br />\n第四，<span style=\"color: red;\">宣布一國兩制死亡</span><br />\n林鄭你咪撚鳩<br />\n你估有冇人儲立緊急法唔等於緊急狀態<br />\n外國政府清楚曬港共嘅極權<br />\n以為咁就冇人上街？<br />\n多撚謝你同一眾智障嘅無知<br />\n<br />\n第五，<span style=\"color: red;\">偽勇武全面退場</span><br />\nFull gear偽勇武不嬲係企最前第一個走<br />\n直接影響軍心<br />\n家下仲蒙面果啲已經有曬覺悟<br />\n反而做事會快、狠、準<br />\n建議偽勇武主力做文宜工作或擔遮<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">祝願十八區遍地開花、不流血、不被捕。香港人加油</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a824af6e6b6818dff9d06625be30f49b9d4c97e8","tid":1623650,"uid":80528,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:45:34.000Z","msg":"邊撚到利 你以後出街個垃圾差佬睇你唔順超就拉鳩你 雖然依家都係<br />\n但立完佢以後攞正牌拉鳩你WO CHING"},{"pid":"6437e6e598f096afc62cb6121e1fd4ec802a21df","tid":1623650,"uid":83732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a824af6e6b6818dff9d06625be30f49b9d4c97e8","tid":1623650,"uid":80528,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:45:34.000Z","msg":"邊撚到利 你以後出街個垃圾差佬睇你唔順超就拉鳩你 雖然依家都係<br />\n但立完佢以後攞正牌拉鳩你WO CHING"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:48:41.000Z","msg":"請花少少時間睇下內文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ed837b3eefba640bdbcfb6a06cb83093d881db","tid":1623650,"uid":83732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:52:11.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"d03100c01e6f23cdc3b69e0c3b416b4a7750d1d8","tid":1623650,"uid":146621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:54:29.000Z","msg":"快 狠 準<br />\n一語中的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1785227d9c72bc5afc86db564e4f3c098c0efd25","tid":1623650,"uid":761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:55:39.000Z","msg":"快狠準<br />\n對準目標裝修"},{"pid":"32837e77bf534e19cfa1a253c1dd8c5948b0ac3f","tid":1623650,"uid":42870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:58:36.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"4879dadbfeffb5720c997ccd981d3d51eb75e9a3","tid":1623650,"uid":42870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a824af6e6b6818dff9d06625be30f49b9d4c97e8","tid":1623650,"uid":80528,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:45:34.000Z","msg":"邊撚到利 你以後出街個垃圾差佬睇你唔順超就拉鳩你 雖然依家都係<br />\n但立完佢以後攞正牌拉鳩你WO CHING"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:00:40.000Z","msg":"你都無睇內文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c8c07bd5cfbdc7b45ea0b035f88bdee814b661e","tid":1623650,"uid":83732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d03100c01e6f23cdc3b69e0c3b416b4a7750d1d8","tid":1623650,"uid":146621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:54:29.000Z","msg":"快 狠 準<br />\n一語中的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:02:11.000Z","msg":"唔作無謂佔領留守<br />\nBe water <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c758465fa651e2b956c2836b7cd17b3c0fa0c386","tid":1623650,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:02:32.000Z","msg":"Solomon叫臨時政府收皮<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1623561\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1623561</a><br />\n<br />\n本身tweet佢個個係想希望佢支持<br />\n但solomon睇到覺得唔妥先話係spy<br />\n已經提曬水"},{"pid":"a842a68fbdc74fbd050080e1a4a4bddc87251a9d","tid":1623650,"uid":83732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:05:52.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"3a704467e2a50c7c6dc36daeb12d775bf2585c37","tid":1623650,"uid":83732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:11:32.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"21f7655c63f0fa686750a3087aabb92fa53c2f5f","tid":1623650,"uid":173640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:17:26.000Z","msg":"總之裝修完就走"},{"pid":"be6f4125ea9db43d44b7f708ba131793bc68cd4a","tid":1623650,"uid":83732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"21f7655c63f0fa686750a3087aabb92fa53c2f5f","tid":1623650,"uid":173640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:17:26.000Z","msg":"總之裝修完就走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:21:52.000Z","msg":"咁多舖頭需要裝修<br />\n唔洗偏心一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d808216f5d614405cf95ebb4f64d7e09b7342e","tid":1623650,"uid":83732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:27:05.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"8fdbe1925e0488f426da48bb05faa0122f18771a","tid":1623650,"uid":261183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:28:31.000Z","msg":"你做到既野其實好簡單，就係日日都戴口罩出街。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1623641\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1623641